<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9376] RawValueTransformerFactory ([json] &amp; [xml]) don&apos;t work in SolrCloud</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9376</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9314&quot; title=&quot;Add all known transformers to TestRandomFlRTGCloud and fix any bugs found&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-9314&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-9314&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I discovered that RawValueTransformerFactory (which powers the &lt;tt&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;xml&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;json&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; doc transformers) doesn&apos;t work with distributed requests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This affects both regular searches, as well as RTG (committed or uncommitted)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
